<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.8">
<l>māṉmuṉin torukāl varicilai vaḷaitta</l>
<l>maṉṉavaṉ poṉṉiṟat turavōṉ</l>
<l>ūṉmuṉin tavaṉa tuṭaliru piḷavā</l>
<l>vukirnuti maṭuttaya ṉaraṉait</l>
<l>tāṉmuṉin tiṭṭa ventiṟal cāpan</l>
<l>tavirttavaṉ tavampurin tuyarnta</l>
<l>māmuṉi koṇarnta kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who bent a striped bow one time, raging against a deer,</l>
<l rend="indent">having raged against</l>
<l>The flesh of the powerful gold-hued one, having gouged his body</l>
<l rend="indent">into two pieces with the tips of [his] claw,</l>
<l>The one who removed the harsh, strong curse which the Unborn,</l>
<l rend="indent">raging, put on Hara,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges which an exalted,</l>
<l rend="indent">great sage brought, having done penance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
